"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"The price of crude oil has changed a lot because of the ongoing war in the Middle East. This situation is causing uncertainty in the market.\",            \"english_title\": \"Oil Price Changes\",            \"translated_version\": \"El precio del petr\u00f3leo ha cambiado mucho por la guerra en el Medio Oriente. Esto causa incertidumbre en el mercado.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Cambios en Precio del Petr\u00f3leo\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Lawsuits in California claim that OpenAI and Sam Altman were negligent and contributed to a mass shooting by not monitoring the suspect's ChatGPT activity.\",            \"english_title\": \"OpenAI Lawsuits\",            \"translated_version\": \"Demandas en California dicen que OpenAI y Sam Altman fueron negligentes y ayudaron a un tiroteo masivo por no vigilar la actividad de ChatGPT del sospechoso.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Demandas contra OpenAI\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Russia has announced that the annual event to remember the Soviet victory in World War Two will not include military vehicles or cadets this year.\",            \"english_title\": \"Russia's Event Change\",            \"translated_version\": \"Rusia anunci\u00f3 que el evento anual para recordar la victoria sovi\u00e9tica en la Segunda Guerra Mundial no tendr\u00e1 veh\u00edculos militares ni cadetes este a\u00f1o.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Cambio en Evento de Rusia\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Prosecutors have accused Cole Tomas Allen of trying to assassinate President Donald Trump and argue that he should stay in custody until his trial.\",            \"english_title\": \"Assassination Attempt\",            \"translated_version\": \"Fiscales acusaron a Cole Tomas Allen de intentar asesinar al Presidente Donald Trump y dicen que debe quedarse en custodia hasta su juicio.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Intento de Asesinato\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Authorities have linked the Coco platform to serious crimes like child abuse, drug offenses, rape, and murder.\",            \"english_title\": \"Coco Platform Crimes\",            \"translated_version\": \"Autoridades han vinculado la plataforma Coco a cr\u00edmenes serios como abuso infantil, delitos de drogas, violaci\u00f3n y asesinato.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Cr\u00edmenes de Plataforma Coco\"        }    ]}"